[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="ZoneDef" load_steps=2 format=3]

; W3-T7 Stage 1 — S2 ZoneDef authoring (Part A only; ticket `86c9y7ygj`).
;
; This file is the geographic SHELL — anchors + procedural_slot_pool are
; left empty per the Stage 1 dispatch brief. Parts B (S2 mobs), C (S2
; chunks), and D (S2 boss room) ship in later PRs.
;
; Sponsor-locked S2 names (2026-05-24): melee mob = Bone-Catalyst.
; This zone is the mid-stratum exploration zone — the "archive proper"
; where the Bone-Catalyst melee archetype first appears alongside the
; ranged Sunken-Scholar from z2. Pressure escalates here; quest_target
; anchor likely placed here in Part C per Track 3 exploration-quest
; design (post-wave3-sequencing.md §1 Commitment 3).
;
; TODO Part C: populate `anchors` (entry + ≥1 exit + quest_target slot)
; and `procedural_slot_pool` with mid-tier combat chunks containing both
; Sunken-Scholar + Bone-Catalyst mob spawns per FloorAssembler.
;
; Cross-references:
;   team/drew-dev/level-chunks.md § "Zone schema" + § "S2 zone roster"
;   team/uma-ux/palette-stratum-2.md (S2 doctrine palette)

